{"he9188c5dge986g419cgaffbg38e4eabd8002": ["Morning. I hope last night's little unpleasantness hasn't left a bad taste in your-", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "870c29e8-3891-420a-d717-295c1440e0bd"], "h50c1a2aeg54ebg4bb1gae78gde553482e6d1": ["Well. I hope there are no bad feelings.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "3a967f5a-4e86-0bc1-50a0-2482e94740a6"], "hf73bc0f7gddcbg47a2gbff9g4b0aa9de3ed6": ["Not at all. Having a vampire on our side could be useful.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "320912dc-b90b-b18f-3c03-1065a6600d5f"], "hf856ccf3g131ag4c56gb6c2g25951b1ea22a": ["Indeed it could. These are very helpful in a fight.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "9a16648b-bcb3-3f76-daf0-956dafc923c3"], "he7b324f9g12a4g4905g971eg17726c562e0c": ["Of course, I can't summon wolves or turn to mist like a 'true' vampire. Being a spawn has its drawbacks.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "8ef5aa89-b3fe-144d-2b26-72c3919b2558"], "ha23d378fg101eg4242g865ege398973491ad": ["Is that how you can stand in the sun? Because you're not a 'true' vampire?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "96f3f5a6-4277-05a7-f64d-b39073b59c27"], "he3dae185g709cg4763g8a0bgd49b3bb11531": ["Oh no, I should be cinders in this light. I hadn't seen the sun for two hundred years before we crashed here.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "55f3c89b-5fbf-ec83-24bd-e82ae701a465"], "h4b5b6821g06f4g4265gbff7gc7c9131edc47": ["Someone - or something - wants me alive. They've changed the rules.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "59dd5dbb-e242-fa8f-2800-7a0f0e496529"], "h174224aegee93g427fg9c44g82d947b145c1": ["Some of the rules, at least. I can enter homes uninvited, but running water still burns like acid.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "a3f7874c-7d42-c206-2747-7a297303c6d2"], "hdf2814e2gf6e0g457dgb999g85f1d5955e94": ["As for my other quirks - well, we can figure those out in time.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "4c3117f7-3d54-ec4b-21b8-40fb05131cec"], "hb3aec910gb068g4e3ag82c1g5c0562331cd8": ["What's causing this? The mind flayer's parasite?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "0af28beb-2830-0c56-41fc-096e4a06f050"], "hcd2fb315gc9e0g45bfgb7c4g3125dfed93f5": ["That's my theory, but who knows?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "6ceaf9af-4a2a-a083-f4dd-03d74f82de5f"], "h3c39efd2g8175g4ef4g8de9g40a4bf1e47a0": ["I'm just glad you're being sensible about these revelations. I was worried people might turn up with torches and pitchforks.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "0f404f48-9d4a-de67-05ce-46ee8227463c"], "h09612ff4g7931g43efgbb66g52f4d75bea3a": ["Although there's still time.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "7dd1814a-beed-c273-5e51-a23836aeaf14"], "h56560057g9ab4g417fgb9a0gf7fca458c1f6": ["A vampire among us? So be it.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "a4795f13-4172-f27a-7cf7-815429f838b8"], "hcbb4484fg408dg4a24ga54fg32a121a27980": ["But should I wake with so much as a drop of blood on my neck, I will <i>end</i> him.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "8cf00b81-c0c2-0e59-2bdb-b0f54b2fb14d"], "h1db595a8g1304g4ebcgb314gd97b90bcc06c": ["A vampire? Well that explains the pallor. ", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "4a7a00b5-1d7f-ec46-e9da-6329a37bff3d"], "h824667bcg494bg45e0g8839gc7d964e11632": ["Given our group's nature, I don't see much harm. We're each monsters in the making, after all.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "d1b32e25-a835-683d-fe72-41989bba9331"], "h8b1d9802g84bbg4750gaa5cgbb3d71f12bae": ["|So, he's a vampire?|", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "8cc06568-311a-48a5-baed-cf369ff6527c"], "h3b2a739eg2945g4ca8gaf50g610e558eed40": ["|I have opinions about this!|", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "a259f59d-fae9-e202-77c1-24a30e135917"], "h1262db67g461ag4b0fga455g27266f4a8165": ["|So, he's a vampire?|", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "d083d46b-6f11-4c2e-b959-e0ec480136f9"], "he72c8c74g1c92g4bd9g9cfeg47b59c932525": ["|I have opinions about this!|", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "3ec21126-94a8-ecbb-b183-b43241a9d651"], "h0cc71c52gcc47g4324g9ae6ged51195d92e3": ["|So, he's a vampire?|", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "76cc51b3-e4bc-429c-889c-5f7e871bc9a4"], "h3ad669e5gfe35g4819g80b8g4af7acb9c644": ["|I have opinions about this!|", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "9bd918fe-e2b2-0bef-0934-e921345da996"], "hff82d459g024bg453bg8a6cg919c4d56a948": ["Hunting with vampires? Never thought I'd see the day.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "88841826-9e51-ddc9-5167-d783b5e15599"], "h00dd2aadge3ecg4ad4g8f1eg78680656e52f": ["Very well - but I'm keeping an eye on you. And no wisecracks about having us for supper.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "4ee88066-396a-7d45-93cf-6c30388a8dcb"], "hd88a27e6g987dg444dg87ecgd856e1dd3235": ["So we're travelling with a vampire, are we? Of course we are.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "c2275a91-f0bc-40cd-9ca3-903bf5af6aa0"], "ha1be9e13g73e4g4552g8417g471eeaf33ece": ["A word of warning, Astarion: I taste absolutely <i>awful</i>.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "e9df6490-f31d-66bc-e24e-138938c7d9bb"], "hafad6e8dg68fcg450dg824ag11771eff2e9e": ["For his sake, he best not develop an appetite for githyanki.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "185a99cf-ad61-9465-dd50-9703afc71059"], "h395aa3d5gd152g42c8g92efge1e5d3c930f0": ["I'd just better not wake in the night to find fangs at my throat.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "e348aafa-79cf-9dde-4fb1-ff870f9d7247"], "h786e3ee8ga5a9g458dgb877g9faf276e0360": ["|I have opinions too|", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "5577482b-7f8c-4bf6-a3d4-a01ab3d9167f"], "hdf713ceegb3eeg45eag9601ga2ca08726635": ["|I have opinions too|", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "44fd0dcc-9be1-4ce7-948b-b0c04148ac54"], "h0d4fae97g1a1cg4c3ag94b7ga1b8d17ef90b": ["|I have opinions too|", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "83c4fa3c-6f95-4459-8112-09d4e43d1c71"], "h56de64d9gf788g454fgab6fgb1cc808fcc8a": ["Fine - as long as he keeps his fangs off our necks.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "71f289c5-31aa-4ae1-9ca5-ef21b8f7327e"], "h09d7d0f2ga2dfg45e0g88c0g53a71210a70c": ["Oh, and a quick word of warning, Astarion: I taste absolutely <i>awful</i>. Keep your distance.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "4acd8104-2860-4fe7-9b25-0523ff462b99"], "hbedadf19gdf09g4a11ga71ag185bf0fd236b": ["Enough. We need him, like it or not.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "0f67c7c7-51c6-23a3-6e5e-57174b6a2377"], "hfeaa61e9gcfb3g44bdga6bbg3d467dee8b4f": ["He's not wrong. We're bound together, no matter what comes.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "9f83acae-f6f5-95bb-c7ce-0798c779de0f"], "h67794f71gb053g4a9eg8644g980f06428c7f": ["She's not wrong. We're bound together, no matter what comes.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "9f83acae-f6f5-95bb-c7ce-0798c779de0f"], "h4e120fc6gb7eag4b22gade6g849d47501a61": ["There now. We're all friends again.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "4c175747-8b18-0ec9-98cf-9cfa8b9646be"], "ha5eebaa1g11d4g418dgad82gb4425bafcb6f": ["Shall we go? There's a long day ahead of us.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "7f7b2aae-13aa-e42f-781b-ee8e85affacc"], "h57dfb45ag52e2g4ec9g9354g5176f95faa6b": ["|Reaction to player keeping Astarion.|", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "f50ee143-1322-516c-2ece-2834b40c1fb4"], "hd7ff23eegf2e8g4c57g9e50g20d94820d0ad": ["|Reaction to player keeping Astarion.|", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "b23b4ee8-feb6-bde3-609e-c97416f1251b"], "hf6ae5256gd7aag4b75g91b9g1462c500205a": ["|Reaction to player keeping Astarion.|", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "06c8f769-7939-c0fa-f475-4432dfbf4e3f"], "hedd7002dg78ddg4112ga277g9f0cd91ae471": ["I just better not wake with any holes in my neck.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "0f385318-f324-e233-74eb-0ad751f218fc"], "ha6c67389g1824g41f0g928cg6235154eafc1": ["You say all the right words, but I'm not so sure you mean the right things. Still, I will respect the decision that was made.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "2d648735-0477-2f2f-3abb-b92efbf6f3fa"], "he2f7a93cg57bbg41c8ga43fg12c36109c9e0": ["I trust him. He won't hurt us.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "f9a296b8-8301-1f69-e681-e1132199dbd0"], "h0c586ff8ge90ag431agbedbg891fcda13c7d": ["Quite the opposite. I'm here in the spirit of openness and honesty, to work together as a team.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "d671cc2a-7b0e-dd91-1922-b4cd59684b9c"], "hc3a99ae7gf395g486cg93f9g9be6aa1e5bf7": ["If you don't like it, you can leave.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "76b1f538-f90e-33d8-2e61-c74e0093c564"], "h2166173dg6f97g49c6g9f64gc5d99d9e4cd1": ["I wouldn't recommend it. I won't get you, but the mind flayers might.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "425f8c11-252f-2458-757a-a9d707042b9d"], "h1fbba1eeg4136g4f82gbd9ag0884322917c1": ["|Comment on situation!|", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "08414d63-d573-41c5-91a9-72fe2ed15301"], "hc020df0fgca6cg45b8g99b9gef42e1813472": ["|I have opinions about this!|", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "5db94ba7-438a-1923-9490-d8aa72467236"], "h432fd9a1gda02g45a4ga720g6a8747c5d7f1": ["|Comment on situation!|", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "def1e5e7-046f-4eb0-94c9-895a7d2fca29"], "had142167g3142g4493g9fcfg056b62b0f8ea": ["|I have opinions about this!|", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "5f5af428-1445-a7f8-148b-8951c3f79378"], "hab921e53gacd1g4c89g8520gd1b0c39c27ef": ["|Comment on situation!|", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "42aa7043-a63e-4eaf-b24b-43e672620f59"], "h12d470ebg7954g4c49gbac5g9b3171b1b785": ["|I have opinions about this!|", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "86e8c25c-5962-e6a6-9ff1-7d8351da835f"], "h054d9a05g1834g430cg9448g339b93e4c5e5": ["So we're travelling with a vampire, are we?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "348a0cbf-48df-42f2-9521-490d360dce54"], "h30104cacg9ab0g4ce1ga4f1g06426ea943c2": ["A word of warning, Astarion: I taste absolutely <i>awful</i>. Keep your distance.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "79e35825-9259-6f5a-3023-b7a669e47a94"], "h53735371gbc64g44e8gb08ag20017bf60ea6": ["If I can help, just ask. We're in this together.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "c415ef2c-6e97-3a58-7f0d-152dae27688c"], "h37fef8c1ge9abg464dga667g5c365fbcb834": ["Oh you're such a sweetheart.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "244d6a14-80e0-48e2-aac2-8e2d11d7471f"], "h739742d1gf429g4526ga746g4ea61ac5e259": ["Figure them out quickly. I don't want any more surprises.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "40f3da95-d277-7011-2143-24d31efb5d66"], "hda712fbag2999g4100g9bbag7cfc90cf53be": ["No more surprises. You have my word.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "74b75238-c35b-ed43-dea5-948c664f8036"], "h22fc8253g95eeg4287ga49dg265ea587a230": ["Some of the rules, at least. Running water still burns like acid, and I don't know if I need an invitation to enter a house.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "53106f28-b8a1-f04b-9431-91ef90fda7a8"], "h9269a912g70a0g4ae4ga6b2g63cbe9548727": ["Any other drawbacks I should know about?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "dbab3495-6273-155d-837e-f6ea42a75450"], "h6a00475bg8d97g43d4ga149gd4daaf9b7cd3": ["Oh, I've no idea. For two hundred years, the sun would have turned me to cinders. Until the crash, when I woke up bathed in its light.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "e188c0f7-4f53-d729-9f09-1a706b9c2d48"], "h0783e027g7809g4e3dgb2b6gb54b9f4f2ab6": ["Pity. I thought you'd be more powerful.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "905a7474-7f0b-b308-f875-690dcd9cff67"], "hb89a27e0gefb9g45b2g8e88g1a4358f3994e": ["Perhaps I am. For two hundred years, the sun would have turned me to cinders. Now I stand here like it's nothing.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "0fffe487-0176-52fb-10ec-2d951565e18c"], "h94b53ae1g7241g4c94ga38bgc6a6a879c75d": ["No, but I have questions. How are you standing in the sun?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "0d631f28-4d6e-fd51-7f23-b375b1dd2930"], "ha1018eefg6957g4b15ga4b9g2daee699f7a5": ["Oh, I have no idea. By rights I should be cinders in this light. But someone - or something - is keeping me alive.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "beb79fff-053c-ee7d-1d66-1dc64d1cfca8"], "h14f2ce90g0f18g4daeg80f6gfd644cab00e7": ["You're lucky I didn't kill you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "635178ff-f1f1-65e5-52b9-09a2e216667e"], "hc32f2c0ag65edg4d81g992bgf0ee225118d2": ["And you're lucky I'm not a 'true' vampire. Last night could have gone very differently if I'd magically summoned a pack of wolves.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "740dbe0b-7fb1-fe0f-bfce-99e82f9cb28d"], "h6549a562gb199g43c2gb01ag0474e3dd615a": ["Alas, I'm just a spawn. All of the hunger, few of the powers.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "70d249f8-0313-79aa-4c1a-6fc1e7dcb178"], "h61bf70f7g2ff9g4613g8efdgd73c7d187027": ["Good morning. How do you feel?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "18f826bf-1119-4786-9919-3ebeeae4d80c"], "h98817d06g757dg4f35g97acgcba8c4a93881": ["I'm fine, I just feel a little woozy.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "540a3ec3-71fa-6d13-aa93-18d307962f44"], "h8c22cc7dg467cg4677g899fg4861eb3252ef": ["It'll pass. Just be glad I'm not a 'true' vampire.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "ecbd68ee-c59f-4096-7e49-2041f3768b95"], "hf3afaa06ge27eg46bfg9079ga6593a11b4df": ["A bite from them and you might wake up as a vampire spawn, like my good self. All of a vampire's hunger, but few of their powers.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "a3fbd3b4-55dc-bb87-7850-bc79ceb6b197"], "h18c57afag370ag46c8g81f0g1a4263fcce9b": ["My neck hurts, how do you think I feel?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "2ad0da68-28ee-122a-eed8-ad74846a95bb"], "hc21c9ec6g7178g447bg9f2ag1d49aff9b473": ["Be grateful I'm not a 'true' vampire, then.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "829f5c16-b09f-87c7-ad8c-14d5e21b7af2"], "he4b912fcg2a08g484ag8efag2e3267162111": ["I feel awful. We won't be doing that again.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "046676f0-d512-729c-d6ad-fbee8a0b2127"], "h0c9efa5bgfe5fg4345g9178g1bc8405c5abf": ["A pity. Just be grateful I'm not a 'true' vampire.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_AstarionHungerC_CRD_Astarion_MorningAfter.html", "ab4bb3f6-673e-d852-3f4b-e5926e1a7627"]}